[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11017] refactored the 
``flatten``
 command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11001] added an 
``exec``
 command for Windows
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10940] refactored 
``Closure``
 captures to use 
``Vec``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10926] refactored env conversion to eliminate 
``Value::follow_cell_path_not_from_user_input``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10925] refactored to use 
``Record::get``
 instead of 
``Value``
 functions
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10903] refactored 
``drop columns``
 to fix issues
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11013] refactored 
``transpose``
 and improve perf
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11004] added 
``Record::truncate``
 for trimming based on len
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11002] added 
``Record::drain``
 to take out elements by range
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10930] refactored 
``table``
 cmd and 
``nu-table``
 with Record API
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10929] refactored 
``find``
 in terms of clean 
``Record``
 API
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10928] used record API in more parts of 
``nu-protocol``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10927] used 
``Record``
's public API in a bunch of places
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10896] refactored+fixed 
``Config``
<-
>
``Value``
 mechanism
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10992] fixed the Alpine docker file
drbrain 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10991] converted ShellError::DatetimeParseError to named fields
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10984] matched toolkit clippy settings to CI clippy settings
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10971] converted ShellError::UnsupportedInput to named fields
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10954] restored test_config tests
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10952] showed plugin extra usage and search terms
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10865] updated description and error types for 
``split-by``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10990] allowed vscode-specific ansi escape sequence to set path
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10980] allowed 
``items``
 to properly evaluate block settings
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10976] updated an 
``items``
 example to send data through the pipeline
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10966] removed unnecessary files
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10965] updated 
``trash``
 dependency to 3.1.2
, and 
